          <Vi>đặc thù, cụ thể, rõ ràng</Vi>
          <En>Real and distinct; not abstract or theoretical.</En>
          <Example>The evidence presented was concrete and irrefutable.</Example>
          <IsArchaic>false</IsArchaic>
          <Situations>
            <Situation id="4d3a179a-40a3-445a-aaa7-91381ebf8ee1">
