          <En>A hard, heavy material made by mixing cement, sand, gravel, and water, used for building.</En>
          <Example>The workers poured concrete to lay the foundation.</Example>
          <IsArchaic>false</IsArchaic>
          <Situations>
            <Situation id="d8cdbb61-1c6d-471c-a598-8b2072f1f53c">
